    "通常2〜5分かかります。このまましばらくお待ちください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dies dauert normalerweise 2–5 Minuten. Bitte warten."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This usually takes 2–5 minutes. Please wait."
          }
        },
